@host=http://localhost:{{$dotenv SERVER_PORT}}

### Get available datasets
GET {{host}}/v1/dataset
### Get dataset metadata
GET {{host}}/v1/dataset/skyalps-flight-data
### Get from http source
GET {{host}}/v1/dataset/sta-time-tables/raw
### Get from ftp source
GET {{host}}/v1/dataset/skyalps-flight-data/raw

### List all datasets with realtime feeds
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime
### Get realtime feed metadata for a dataset
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime/sta-time-tables
### Get trip updates feed (JSON)
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime/sta-time-tables/trip-updates
### Get vehicle positions feed (JSON)
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime/sta-time-tables/vehicle-positions
### Get service alerts feed (JSON)
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime/sta-time-tables/service-alerts
### Request protobuf format via Accept header (returns 406 until pb sources are configured)
GET {{host}}/v1/realtime/sta-time-tables/trip-updates
Accept: application/x-protobuf
